```plantuml
@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle AWS {
  rectangle "S3 Bucket" as S3 #aliceblue
  rectangle "SQS Queue" as SQS #lightsteelblue
  rectangle "SNS Topic" as SNS #lightyellow
  rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGateway #mistyrose
  rectangle "Aurora PostgreSQL" as AuroraDB #palegreen

  rectangle "Lambda Functions" as Lambdas {
    rectangle "waze-data-download" as DownloadLambda #lightcyan
    rectangle "waze-data-process" as ProcessLambda #lightgoldenrodyellow
    rectangle "waze-data-alerts-processing" as AlertsLambda #lightpink
    rectangle "waze-data-jams-processing" as JamsLambda #lightseagreen
    rectangle "waze-data-irregularities-processing" as IrregularitiesLambda #lightcoral
    rectangle "waze-db-initialize" as DBInitLambda #lightgray
    rectangle "waze-data-api" as APILambda #lavender
  }
}

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> APIGateway : Access API

APIGateway --> APILambda : Route request
APILambda --> AuroraDB : Query data

DownloadLambda --> S3 : Store raw JSON data
S3 --> ProcessLambda : Trigger processing on new data

ProcessLambda --> SQS : Send message for processing
SQS --> AlertsLambda : Deliver message for alerts processing
SQS --> JamsLambda : Deliver message for jams processing
SQS --> IrregularitiesLambda : Deliver message for irregularities processing

AlertsLambda --> AuroraDB : Store processed data
JamsLambda --> AuroraDB : Store processed data
IrregularitiesLambda --> AuroraDB : Store processed data

DBInitLambda --> AuroraDB : Initialize and manage schema

ProcessLambda --> SNS : Notify about processing status
SNS --> User : Send notification

@enduml
```